Restaurant and Pizza API
Description

A Flask-based RESTful API for managing restaurants, pizzas, and their relationships.
Getting Started
Prerequisites

    Python
    Flask

Installation

    Clone the repository:
git clone <repository_url>
cd <repository_directory>

Install dependencies:


pip install -r requirements.txt

Set up the database:


flask db init
flask db migrate
flask db upgrade

Populate the database:

python populate_db.py

Start the server:
flask run

The API runs locally at http://localhost:5000.
API Endpoints

    Get All Restaurants: /restaurants
    Get Restaurant by ID: /restaurants/<int:id>
    Delete Restaurant: /restaurants/<int:id>
    Create Restaurant-Pizza Relationship: /restaurant_pizzas

Sample Data

The API includes sample data.
Dependencies

    Flask
    SQLAlchemy